      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, ensuring direct engagement and a visceral driving experience. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a limited-slip M-differential that provides excellent traction out of corners. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior displays minor stone chips and age-appropriate patina, the performance remains uncompromising with a taut suspension geometry and responsive hydraulic steering. A well-sorted enthusiast's machine optimized for the B-roads.",
